text: Ulf Adolf Roger Dinkelspiel (4 July 1939 - 9 January 2017) was a Swedish politician and financier. He was a member of the Moderate Party. He served as the Minister of European Affairs and Foreign Trade from 1991 to 1994. He was born in Stockholm. Dinkelspiel died from cancer on 9 January 2017 in Stockholm.
